Package wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.dragon.loot.elements

Class DragonLootElementEgg

java.lang.Object
wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.dragon.loot.elements.DragonLootElementEgg
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDragonLootElement
public class DragonLootElementEgg
extends Object
implements IDragonLootElement
An implementation of IDragonLootElement to represent a dragon egg. This element can be generated as either an item in an inventory or as a block in the world.
Author:
Parker Hawke - Choco
